                        <p>On the provision of training services at the Montessori center, hereinafter referred to as the "School", to any individual, hereinafter referred to as the "Student".</p>
                        <p>This agreement is a public contract-offer according to Art. 633 of the Civil Code of Ukraine, is equivalent to a bilateral agreement, and, in accordance with the current legislation of Ukraine, has proper legal force from the moment of full and unconditional acceptance of the terms of this Agreement (Offer) and its Appendices by the user.</p>
